  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "This is no ordinary forest. Then again, this is no ordinary Little Red Riding Hood. She can sure throw a kick, and let me tell you, she needs it to get to grandma safely. The forest is filled with wicked goblins, snakes, scorpions, bears and of course, the WOLF. Team up with her faithful dog and help LITTLE RED RIDING HOOD collect fruit, candy and magic potions so that she can fight these evil beasts and save grandma!",
